title: @Phreak / Riot Dash; Thanks for the game
body: I didn't get a chance to say it before you guys left, but it was an honor to play with you guys. I somehow feel accomplished after having a match with 2 of the most well known names in league, even if we didn't talk much. Thanks again :D

replies.body: did you do TONS OF DAMAGE?

Hmm, Idk. What qualifies as tons of damage now adays? I'd say yes; I just checked the charts and I was 2nd highest damage behind the jinx I got fed. I was support Lux (cause thats the only way I ever play her)
